1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:37,399 --> 00:00:41,920
Why bother Your Highness
over a legend?

3
00:00:42,039 --> 00:00:43,799
Since divine medicine can heal you,

4
00:00:43,799 --> 00:00:45,039
it is good news.

5
00:00:45,679 --> 00:00:47,240
But it seems to me

6
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:50,119
that you don't want your hand
to heal quickly.

7
00:00:50,439 --> 00:00:54,320
Could it be you don't want
to embroider for me anymore?

8
00:00:54,439 --> 00:00:55,679
How could that be, Your Highness?

9
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:58,159
My skill is superb,

10
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:02,159
but only you can realize
the beauty I imagine.

11
00:01:03,119 --> 00:01:06,200
No one else has your grace and poise.

12
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:08,480
Then stop refusing.

13
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:11,599
I've heard the tale
Ms. Meng mentioned.

14
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,359
It's just a divine prescription.

15
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:15,920
I'll ask for it.

16
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:17,719
Thank you, Your Highness.

17
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:46,860
=Episode 9=

18
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:48,640
(Jingyuan Manor)

19
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,560
(Jingyuan Manor)
Feeling better, Ruoheng?

20
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:55,519
You've already worried so much
about the Flower Festival.

21
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,159
Yet you still think of me.

22
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:59,000
I'm truly ashamed.

23
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:02,439
From now on, I'll follow every rule,

24
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:03,560
waiting for the Prince's return.

25
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:05,200
It's good you understand.

26
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,239
By the way,

27
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:09,199
I've heard the Cheng'en Manor

28
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:11,120
has a prescription for burns.

29
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,319
Do you know it?

30
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:17,039
Your Highness. Lord Cheng'en
received it from a divine healer.

31
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,919
There is such a prescription.

32
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:23,719
Why bring this up, Wenyue?

33
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:26,479
Meng Wan mentioned it
when presenting the garment.

34
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,719
She's quite loyal to Wu Lian.

35
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,479
Now that he's kneeling and injured,

36
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,919
has your anger subsided?

37
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:38,080
You are a noble lady.

38
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:40,719
Why lower yourself to bicker
with a merchant?

39
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,479
Let bygones be bygones.

40
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,639
Show the grace of a lady.

41
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:49,159
So you want the prescription
from my family?

42
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,039
It's best you understand.

43
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,159
If not,

44
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:55,319
I'll send someone to fetch it.

45
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,840
No trouble at all.

46
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:01,360
No need. I have it.

47
00:03:01,599 --> 00:03:03,360
I just don't want to give it
to Wu Lian.

48
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:05,639
The Prince returns in a few days.

49
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,759
You'll be a bride soon.

50
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:08,520
Ruoheng,

51
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:11,960
it's time to set aside
your tantrums.

52
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,400
I was joking, Wenyue.

53
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,960
Look how worried you are.

54
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:19,879
I'd give my life for you.

55
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,719
Let alone a prescription.

56
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,240
Sweet talker.

57
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,159
Write it down quickly.

58
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,199
Then let Dr. Li check it.

59
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:31,159
Don't make a foolish mistake.

60
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,000
Got it.

61
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,159
Nanny Du,

62
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,680
come choose some fabric.

63
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:38,520
Have Yanyu Embroidery House
make two new outfits for Ruoheng

64
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,280
as a thank-you gift.

65
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,199
Yes.

66
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,560
Rest now, Ruoheng.

67
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,439
Why did you agree?

68
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:58,439
We don't remember
the whole prescription.

69
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,120
We can't just write anything.

70
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,360
It doesn't matter.

71
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,080
Even if Wu Lian's hand
is really burned,

72
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,319
a prescription for reducing heat

73
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:07,520
will work fine.

74
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,439
But the manor doctor
will check it.

75
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:11,759
It's my house's prescription.

76
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,240
Would he dare question it?

77
00:04:18,220 --> 00:04:19,079
(Topical Medicine)

78
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,120
(Topical Medicine)
This prescription...

79
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,839
Is something wrong?

80
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,720
No, no. Your Highness,

81
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,519
the herbs seem common,

82
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:28,639
but using huzhu as a medicinal guide
is brilliant.

83
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,560
This ingredient is rare.

84
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,199
The healer's genius, surely.

85
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:35,399
Since the prescription is correct,

86
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,199
go treat Master Wu

87
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,240
at Yanyu Embroidery House.

88
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,360
Yes, Your Highness.

89
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:46,639
Nanny Du, Ruoheng did well
providing the medicine.

90
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,800
Seems she's truly sorry.

91
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,199
Lift her house arrest.

92
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,360
Yes.

93
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,160
Black blood?

94
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,519
The medicine is poisoned.

95
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,160
What?

96
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:20,480
I prepared this myself.

97
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:21,920
How could it be poisoned?

98
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:23,639
Dr. Li,

99
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:27,439
my master was poisoned by your medicine.

100
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:29,120
We all saw it.

101
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:32,920
Master Wu, a healer has a conscience.

102
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,959
My reputation is nothing,

103
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,600
but this involves the manor,

104
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:40,480
the Princess Consort,
and the lady who gave the medicine.

105
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,519
Dr. Li,

106
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:45,399
we saw it with our own eyes.

107
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,839
Let's go.

108
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,439
I'm reporting this.

109
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:54,079
Master Wu, I'm just a simple doctor.

110
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,360
I only earn a few coins to get by.

111
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:58,240
I don't know about high rank,

112
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,879
and I don't understand
these power games.

113
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,360
Please, just let me go.

114
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:03,879
Let me go.

115
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:05,160
What a shame.

116
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,319
You're already involved.

117
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:11,079
If you don't want to be
accused of killing me,

118
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,879
do as I say.

119
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:31,680
These herbs are just for reducing heat.

120
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,319
They won't heal burns at all.

121
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:37,199
She scribbled something
to fool the Princess Consort.

122
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:39,040
She wanted me to slip up.

123
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,360
But she was too impatient.

124
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,720
This time,

125
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,160
I'll make her

126
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:48,600
fall into her own trap.

127
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,839
Meng Wan, copy the handwriting
from this prescription.

128
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:56,079
Change a few herbs and give it to Dr. Li.

129
00:06:56,519 --> 00:06:58,079
Yes, Master.

130
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:07,839
How much tighter is the waist
than last month?

131
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,199
Your Highness,

132
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,160
three-tenths of an inch.

133
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:13,040
When the Prince first saw me,

134
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,519
he praised my slim figure.

135
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,040
But now...

136
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,600
Now, you're even lovelier,
Your Highness.

137
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,120
Your Highness! Your Highness!

138
00:07:21,079 --> 00:07:22,240
Master Wu is poisoned!

139
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:23,120
What?

140
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:25,319
Master Wu took the medicine
from Lady Cheng'en's prescription

141
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,240
and was poisoned.

142
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,120
I decocted it myself

143
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,959
and handed it to him.

144
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,959
The fault is with the prescription.

145
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,639
Didn't you examine it?

146
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:35,000
You said it was fine.

147
00:07:36,839 --> 00:07:38,480
I saw that some herbs

148
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,480
had weak toxicity.

149
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:42,800
I thought it was the healer's genius,

150
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:44,240
using poison to fight poison.

151
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,319
But I didn't expect...

152
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:46,120
Useless!

153
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:49,240
Nanny Du, bring her to me.

154
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:49,879
Yes.

155
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:54,000
You dared to poison him?

156
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,959
Poison Wu Lian?

157
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,319
Wenyue, I truly repented.

158
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,680
Why would I poison him?

159
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,399
Someone must be scheming.

160
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:02,639
Let me confront him

161
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,720
to prove my innocence.

162
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,879
He's already poisoned.

163
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:06,240
How can you confront him?

164
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:11,279
Wenyue, since Wu Lian is poisoned,

165
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,759
this is a criminal case.

166
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:15,560
I'll ask Magistrate Yu
to investigate the truth.

167
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:17,120
Fine.

168
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,240
Nanny Du,

169
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,439
tell Yu Ming to go to
Yanyu Embroidery House.

170
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,839
Handle this as a criminal case.

171
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,680
Yes.

172
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,959
Please save my master, Your Highness!

173
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:35,399
My master collapsed after
taking Lady Cheng'en's medicine.

174
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,519
Watch your tongue.

175
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,840
Meng Wan.

176
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,639
Help me up.

177
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:41,399
Master!

178
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,559
Your Highness,

179
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:54,519
forgive me for not rising to greet you.

180
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:58,960
What do you have to say now?

181
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:01,600
Your Highness, please see the truth.

182
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,639
I'm innocent.

183
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:05,200
This prescription was
a gift from a divine healer.

184
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:06,320
How could it be poisonous?

185
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:07,960
If I wanted to poison him,

186
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:10,240
why not do it on the way back
yesterday?

187
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,639
I dare not suspect Lady Cheng'en.

188
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:17,200
Perhaps I did something

189
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,879
to upset her.

190
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:20,279
Thus, this punishment.

191
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,559
Master Wu,

192
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:24,039
I'll find you the best doctor.

193
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,679
Thank you, Your Highness.

194
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,360
My death is nothing.

195
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,840
But I can no longer embroider for you.

196
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:33,519
I've failed you.

197
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:35,200
If you truly feel you've failed,

198
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:37,159
why make things so difficult for me?

199
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:39,799
Remember, I only came
for my cousin's sake.

200
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:41,519
You know you came for me?

201
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,879
The Prince will return
for the wedding in Flower Festival.

202
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,639
It's Jinxiu City's grand event.

203
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:47,519
As a merchant,
he knows what's important.

204
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,519
As a Lady,

205
00:09:48,519 --> 00:09:49,919
you cause trouble again and again.

206
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:50,720
Your Highness,

207
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:55,399
don't fight with Lady Cheng'en
over a commoner like me.

208
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,320
Perhaps I'm just weak

209
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:02,480
to handle
Lady Cheng'en's tonic prescription.

210
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:04,879
Magistrate Yu arrives!

211
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,919
I pay my respects to Your Highness.

212
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,039
Rise.

213
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:11,399
Magistrate Yu,

214
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:14,240
have you found any leads?

215
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:17,720
No matter who broke the law,

216
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,679
the manor will not play favorites.

217
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:22,080
My preliminary examination

218
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:25,919
shows that this prescription
contains aconite.

219
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,120
Master Wu's poisoning

220
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:29,559
seems related to this herb.

221
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,559
Seems?

222
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,399
Magistrate Yu,

223
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:35,360
is this how you serve
as an official?

224
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,679
Please calm down, Your Highness.

225
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:39,320
The Jingyuan Manor
is strict and fair.

226
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:42,039
I will enforce the law impartially.

227
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:45,639
I request Lady Cheng'en to appear
in court.

228
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:48,440
No! My Lady is of noble birth.

229
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,200
How can she go to...?

230
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:49,759
Granted.

231
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,120
This way, My Lady.

232
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:09,399
Master Wu, rest well.

233
00:11:09,799 --> 00:11:10,759
Thank you, Your Highness.

234
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,519
Meng Wan,

235
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,840
see Her Highness out for me.

236
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,679
Yes.

237
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,320
Master.

238
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:19,960
This way, Your Highness.

239
00:11:26,159 --> 00:11:30,639
(Lin Rulan, this time you'll die
knowing the truth.)

240
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:02,220
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

241
00:12:02,460 --> 00:12:05,460
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

242
00:12:06,660 --> 00:12:09,420
♪The past no longer binds♪

243
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:13,620
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

244
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:18,180
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

245
00:12:19,020 --> 00:12:21,900
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

246
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:24,260
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

247
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:28,340
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

248
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:30,940
♪For your faith that never broke♪

249
00:12:31,140 --> 00:12:35,260
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

250
00:12:36,140 --> 00:12:38,060
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

251
00:12:38,060 --> 00:12:42,300
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

252
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,980
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

253
00:12:46,100 --> 00:12:48,740
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

254
00:12:48,740 --> 00:12:51,340
♪One thought turns into ash♪

255
00:12:52,300 --> 00:12:57,660
♪No future left to write♪

256
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:00,540
♪If I never fall♪

257
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,940
♪How could this waiting end♪

258
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:04,300
♪If I bear no scars♪

259
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:06,620
♪How could I challenge fate♪

260
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:08,980
♪I knew there was no way back♪

261
00:13:08,980 --> 00:13:12,980
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

262
00:13:13,100 --> 00:13:15,220
♪For your faith that never broke♪

263
00:13:15,420 --> 00:13:19,380
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

264
00:13:20,340 --> 00:13:22,260
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

265
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:26,660
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

266
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:30,340
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

267
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:32,940
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

268
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:35,300
♪One thought turns into ash♪

269
00:13:36,420 --> 00:13:41,660
♪No future left to write♪

270
00:13:42,540 --> 00:13:44,940
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

271
00:13:46,220 --> 00:13:48,340
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

272
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:52,220
♪If we meet again someday♪

273
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:58,460
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
